data.description: Step into the Wesley Plan, a meticulously designed residence offering an impressive array of features to enhance your living experience. Boasting 5 bedrooms and 3 baths, this home provides ample space and comfort for the modern family.  Upon entry, you're greeted by a main floor that caters to convenience and versatility. A bedroom and full bath on this level offer flexibility, whether for accommodating guests or providing a private retreat. Additionally, a dedicated media room awaits, perfect for entertainment or relaxation.  Entertain in style with the formal dining and living rooms, providing elegant spaces for hosting gatherings and special occasions. The heart of the home lies in the spacious great room, where a fireplace adds warmth and ambiance. This area seamlessly flows into the open kitchen, featuring an island and breakfast area, ideal for casual dining or morning gatherings.  Experience the epitome of luxury with granite countertops and hardwood flooring gracing the foyer, dining room, breakfast area, and kitchen, adding both sophistication and durability to these high-traffic areas.  Retreat to the expansive master suite, a sanctuary within your home, complete with a sitting room and fireplace, creating a tranquil space for relaxation. The master suite is complemented by a walk-in closet and a generously sized master bath, boasting dual vanity with granite countertops, tile flooring, and a separate tub and shower, offering the ultimate in comfort and style.  This meticulously crafted residence combines functionality with refined elegance, providing a space where every detail has been carefully considered to enhance your lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to make the Wesley Plan your own – a luxurious retreat designed to exceed your expectations.
